thread.title: Damian Mifsud

author: Damian Mifsud
title: Damian Mifsud
text:
Purchased a Nikon D5300 from rhinocamera.com. when comparing to other online shops, rhino camera offered the best prices ,packages and delivery.
Once order was made, it only took a couple of days until I received the camera, even though it was beginning of festive period where you might expect a small delay. Properly packaged and secure.
Couldn't be happier with my purchase. Highly recommended
